All Implemented Interfaces:
JoinSyntaxes, Configurable, IdentifierConfiguration, ConnectionDecorator, LoggingConnectionDecorator.SQLWarningHandler
public class AccessDictionary
extends DBDictionary

Dictionary for Access via DataDirect SequeLink and DataDirect ODBC FoxPro driver. This will not work with any other combination of JDBC/ODBC server and ODBC driver.
